steps.response:
Public schema tables (all have RLS enabled; current row estimate: 0):

- `multiplayer_sessions`  
  - PK: `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`)  
  - Key columns: `story_version_id` (uuid), `host_id` (uuid), `status` (enum `pending|active|completed`, default `pending`), `settings` (jsonb), `session_state` (jsonb), `version` (int, default 0), timestamps  
  - FKs: `story_version_id → public.story_versions.id`, `host_id → public.users.id`

- `saves`  
  - PK: `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`)  
  - Key columns: `story_id` (uuid), `user_id` (uuid), `save` (jsonb), `mode` (text, check `solo|multiplayer`, default `solo`), timestamps  
  - FKs: `story_id → public.stories.id`, `user_id → public.users.id`

- `stories`  
  - PK: `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`)  
  - Key columns: `slug` (text, unique), `title` (text), `summary` (text, nullable), `created_by` (uuid, nullable), timestamps  
  - FK: `created_by → public.users.id`

- `story_versions`  
  - PK: `id` (uuid, default `gen_random_uuid()`)  
  - Key columns: `story_id` (uuid), `status` (enum `draft|published`, default `draft`), `outline` (jsonb), `published_at` (timestamptz, nullable), plus config fields (`engine_range`, `shell`, `theme`, `component_lock`), timestamps  
  - FK: `story_id → public.stories.id`

- `users`  
  - PK: `id` (uuid)  
  - Key columns: `username` (text, nullable), `avatar_url` (text, nullable), timestamps  
  - FKs: `id → auth.users.id` (links to Supabase auth)
